videos.description: MSU's Alvin Ellis III scoops up the loose ball after a scramble and buries the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ellis III scoops up the loose ball and buries it from downtown

videos.description: MSU Head Coach Tom Izzo says the Spartans need to get Miles Bridges more involved in the offense in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Tom Izzo says MSU must get Miles Bridges more involved in 2nd half

videos.description: after hitting five 3-pointers in the 1st half,  Alvin Ellis III buries his 6th 3-pointer of the night.
videos.headline: Ellis III knocks down his 6th 3-pointer of the night

videos.description: Marc Loving loses his defender and knocks down the open 3-pointer for OSU.
videos.headline: Loving knocks down the 3-pointer

videos.description: Cassius Winston dribbles in a circle before blowing by defender and knocking down a running shot.
videos.headline: Winston literally dribbles circles around his defender

videos.description: Miles Bridges runs in transition and finishes with a sweet reverse jam on the other end.
videos.headline: Bridges throws down the reverse dunk in MSU's win

videos.description: Miles Bridges overpowers Marc Loving as he drives to the rack and throws it down.
videos.headline: Bridges bullies Loving with a powerful dunk

videos.description: Miles Bridges knocks down a 3-pointer after perfect ball movement leads to him being open from the wing.
videos.headline: Flawless ball movement leads to a 3-pointer for Miles Bridges

videos.description: Kyle Ahrens buries a 3-pointer from the wing to extend MSU's lead late in the game.
videos.headline: Ahrens knocks down a 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Joshua Langford soars for the putback dunk following a miss from Nick Ward.
videos.headline: Langford destroys the rim with an incredible putback dunk

videos.description: Tom Izzo talks road ahead, improvement for MSU.
videos.headline: Tom Izzo talks road ahead, improvement for MSU.

videos.description: Dan Dakich breaks down the performance of MSU's bench in huge win over Ohio State
videos.headline: Dan Dakich breaks down the performance of MSU's bench in huge win over Ohio State
